description:
Performs a boolean NOT operation on the value received via input `a`.

Example:

1. false@0 is received via `a`
2. true@0 is sent via `not`

442847b6-23b9-4ad6-a3f5-cce6e5159644.name: not
442847b6-23b9-4ad6-a3f5-cce6e5159644.description: Sends the negated value of the input `a`.

name: boolean/Not
